author: Jonathan Spencer For Mailonline
title: Theo Walcott scores his 100th Arsenal goal against Suttton | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Theo Walcott scores his 100th Arsenal goal against Suttton in the FA Cup... becoming the 18th Gunner to reach the special landmark Theo Walcott scored Arsenal's second goal of the night as Arsene Wenger's side beat Sutton 2-0 on Monday Walcott was in the right position at the right time to poke homein history to reach a century of goals At Gander Green Lane, the England international became the 18th player at Arsenal to score 100 goals
